        INPUT:

        - ``d`` -- dictionary to determine projection
        - ``det``  --  (default: ``true``) - determinize the result or not
        - ``simplify`` -- (default: ``True``) - if True and if
          det=True, prune and minimize
        - ``verb`` -- boolean (default: ``False``) - activate or
