        the ith coordinate.
        Give a new automaton where labels are replaced by the projection on
        the ith coordinate.

        INPUT:

        - ``i`` -- int - coordinate of projection
        - ``det``  --  (default: ``true``) - determinize or not the result
        - ``simplify`` -- (default: ``True``) - if True and if det=True, prune
